OL,3,CUrgent police CCTV appeal over 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' incidents on Metrolink
OL,5,Ctrams
OL,7,FAn urgent CCTV appeal has been issued
OL,8,Fby police over what they called
OL,9,F'deeply concerning' incidents on
OL,10,FMetrolink trams.
OL,12,FTwo reports of 'indecency' are under
OL,13,Finvestigation - and an image of a man
OL,14,Fpolice want to speak to taken from a
OL,15,FCCTV camera has been issued.
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police has appealed
OL,18,Fto anyone who recognises the man to
OL,19,Fcome forward.
