OL,3,CUrgent police CCTV appeal over 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' incidents on Metrolink
OL,5,Ctrams
OL,7,FIn a statement issued on Sunday, the
OL,8,Fforce said: "Officers investigating
OL,9,Freports of indecency on Metrolink
OL,10,Fservices across Greater Manchester
OL,11,Fwould like to speak to the man in the
OL,12,Fpicture, as we believe he could assist
OL,13,Fus with our enquiries."
OL,15,FThe first incident is said to have
OL,16,Fhappened on the Oldham and Rochdale
OL,17,Fline at around 11.30pm on Friday,
OL,18,FApril 14.
