OL,7,FThe second incident happened on board
OL,8,Fa tram travelling between Victoria
OL,9,FStation and Deansgate Castlefield
OL,10,Fbetween the times of 11.25 and 11.40pm
OL,11,Fthe following day.
OL,13,FPc Carl Kelly, from GMP's Transport
OL,14,FUnit, said: "We are currently
OL,15,Finvestigating two separate incidents
OL,16,Fof indecency that occurred on Greater
OL,17,FManchester's Metrolink tram network.
