OL,3,CUrgent police CCTV appeal over 'deeply
OL,4,Cconcerning' incidents on Metrolink
OL,5,Ctrams
OL,7,F"These incidents are deeply
OL,8,Fconcerning, and we want to reassure
OL,9,Fthe public that we take crimes of this
OL,10,Fnature incredibly seriously.
OL,12,F"No piece of information is too small
OL,13,F` even details that might seem
OL,14,Finsignificant could be vital in
OL,15,Fhelping us identify those responsible.
OL,16,FYour support is crucial in helping us
OL,17,Fto continue to keep our transport
OL,18,Fnetwork safe for everyone who lives
OL,19,Fand works in Greater Manchester."
